The Government's Decisions:

For the purpose of elections under the jurisdiction of the Election Commission of India, the following District B Taluka level posts have been created as per the Government Decision 2015-Elections, 102-Elector, SAMA as indicated before them. These posts have been extended up to the date 28.02.2025 as per the decision of the Government in question. Government approval is being given to continue all these 244 posts from date 01.03.2025 to date 31.08.2025.
